snippet.title: Sonic Racing
snippet.description:
Inspired by the critically acclaimed console title released in May: Team Sonic Racing. 

It features Artificial Intelligence-controlled team members, new tracks, and a number of unlockable characters. 

The road is yours. Take it now!
